				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Recently I started using my "Mark of..." spell line to pull with.  It has increased range, does no damage, and doesn't draw as much aggro as "Root" does.
<br />

<br />
Basically, it's just better for the purpose of pulling single mobs.  I still use "Root" to bust up the chummy mobs.
<br />

<br />
You know what I was thinking the other day?  Why don't caster mobs use "Root" on US?
<br />

<br />
Wouldn't that just be a BOOGER if they did?
<br />

<br />
Think about one of them rooting your melee or your tank and pulling the party away from it!  (Shudder)
<br />

<br />
Not a pretty picture...
