				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The same strategy works well in Deathfist Citadel where there are 2 MOBs per tent.  Root one (I would root the easier so we kill the hardest one first) and the other linked mob comes to the group.  By the time it is dead the second one comes to wiht no additional pull needed).  As suggested get the group to agree and make sure the cleric is not the higher level than the tank or whoever is peeling the aggro.  It helps to have a Wizard who can keep the Mana flow up.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
